=== 亚伦·斯沃茨事件 ===
{{main|亚伦·斯沃茨}}
2013年1月，开放激进分子[[亚伦·斯沃茨|亚伦·斯沃茨]]自杀了。他曾在麻省理工学院附近被捕，因涉嫌通过麻省理工学院的开放存取校园网络下载[[JSTOR|JSTOR]]文章的罪行而面临长达35年的监禁<ref name="SwartzAaronPR">{{cite web
 |url=https://www.justice.gov/archive/usao/ma/news/2011/July/SwartzAaronPR.html
 |title=Alleged Hacker Charged with Stealing Over Four Million Documents from MIT Network
 |author=<!--Unstated, staff writer-->
 |date=2011-07-19
 |website=The United States Attorney's Office: District of Massachusetts
 |publisher=US Department of Justice
 |access-date=2019-09-07
 |url-status=live
 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120526080523/http://www.justice.gov/usao/ma/news/2011/July/SwartzAaronPR.html
 |archive-date=2012-05-26
}}</ref>。

作为回应，麻省理工学院任命哈尔·阿伯尔森领导一项内部调查，对学校在[[联邦调查局|联邦调查局]]起诉亚伦·斯沃茨的过程中的选择和作用进行调查<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/01/15/aaron-swartz-mit_n_2480627.html |date=2013-01-15 |access-date=2013-01-16 |title=Aaron Swartz Case 'Snowballed Out of MIT's Hands,' Source Says |last=Smith |first=Gerry |publisher=Huffington Post}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://web.mit.edu/newsoffice/2013/letter-on-death-of-aaron-swartz.html |date=2013-01-15 |access-date=2013-01-16 |title=President Reif writes to MIT community regarding Aaron Swartz,' Source Says |last=Smith |first=Gerry |publisher=MIT News}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/business/technology/anonymous-hacks-mit-sites-to-post-aaron-swartz-tribute-call-to-arms/2013/01/14/ff6f706c-5e44-11e2-9940-6fc488f3fecd_print.html |date=2013-01-15 |access-date=2013-01-16 |title=Anonymous hacks MIT sites to post Aaron Swartz tribute, call to arms' Source Says |last=Smith |first=Gerry |newspaper=The Washington Post}}</ref>。该报告于2013年7月26日提交。它的结论是，麻省理工学院在法律上没有做错什么，但建议麻省理工学院考虑改变其一些内部政策<ref>{{cite web |url=http://swartz-report.mit.edu/docs/report-to-the-president.pdf |title=Report to the President: MIT and the Prosecution of Aaron Swartz |last=Abelson |first=Hal |website=Massachusetts Institute of Technology |date=2013-07-26 |access-date=2013-08-02}}</ref>。

